      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PURE HAPPINESS (1) has an excellent record over this journey having never missed the placings in three starts, including two wins. Comes off a (17.90) win last time, scoring by 1.75 lengths in a Grade 5 over 324m at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. DESPICABLE PEDRO (2) is better than last start when fourth (22.69) in a Grade 5 at Maitland over 400m. Solid record here including eight wins. One of the main contenders. KEAON BANNER (3) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 324m behind Addison Banner (18.44) in a Grade 5. Form from his last run is proving strong. Shapes as one to consider. AUTUMN BOY (7) warrants respect although new to this distance.",
